          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a knob of <strong>butter alternative </strong>over a medium-low heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced red onion</strong> with a pinch of<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span><strong>salt</strong> and cook for 5 min or until softened</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
