            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>ginger</strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Roughly chop your <strong>creamed coconut</strong> (if required!)</p><p>Combine your <strong>fig relish</strong>, <strong>chopped creamed coconut</strong> and <strong>vegetable stock </strong>with 200ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[300ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[400ml]</span><strong> boiled water</strong> – this is your <strong>figgy</strong> <strong>coconut stock</strong></p><p>Drain and rinse your <strong>chickpeas</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1626683347960-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1626683347960-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
