            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> figgy aubergine curry</strong> over the <strong>spinach & coriander rice </strong>and garnish with the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>coriander</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
